data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Paraiso Estates! This expansive property boasts 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a versatile, huge entertaining room upstairs that promises endless possibilities for use. The home also features a convenient 3-car garage and exceptional curb appeal that invites you in. Inside, the spaciousness of this residence is immediately apparent, offering a bright and airy feel throughout. Each bedroom is generously sized, ensuring ample natural light and comfort. Perfectly situated within walking distance to parks, schools, shopping, and dining options, this home is located in a highly sought-after neighborhood, making it an ideal choice for anyone looking for convenience and luxury. Dont miss out on the opportunity to make this exquisite Paraiso Estates Home yours!
